{"tid":1774613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對家風向由cctvb新聞可見一斑","createTime":"2019-12-08T11:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T11:57:54.000Z","uid":330254,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a76bb1c080a0e44273ba9ebac990f3e64649b86","tid":1774613,"uid":330254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"因為屋企極深藍所以開住cctvb新聞冇得閂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncctvb 6月7月嗰排都係keep住叫手足做 &ldquo;示威者&rdquo;<br />\n跟住到10月就開始轉口風叫手足做 <span style=\"color: red;\">黑衣人</span><br />\n去到今日報遊行訪問人就稱呼佢哋做<span style=\"color: red;\">遊行人士</span><br />\n手足想開路就叫佢哋<span style=\"color: red;\">黑衣人</span> &ldquo;同警方對峙&rdquo;<br />\n而家對家風向好明顯就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然已經係阿媽係女人嘅事實<br />\n但係希望大家記得當初講嘅不分化不篤灰不割蓆嘅精神<br />\n和勇不分 核爆都唔割呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13cd2df75e800bc2b9af1dee844e7c85957700b","tid":1774613,"uid":113136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"不割蓆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;cctvb仆街啦"}]}